                     <interp inst="t17890114-44-defend390" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted, for that he, on the <rs id="t17890114-44-cd209" type="crimeDate">27th of December</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890114-44-off210 t17890114-44-cd209"></join>, <rs id="t17890114-44-off210" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890114-44-off210" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890114-44-off210" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously did make, forge and counterfeit, and cause and procure to be falsely made, forged, and counterfeited, and willingly act and assist in the false making, forging, and counterfeiting, a certain bill of exchange; commonly called an inland bill of exchange, purporting to have been drawn by one 
                     <persName id="t17890114-44-person391">
                        James
                         Kingdom
                     <interp inst="t17890114-44-person391" type="surname" value="Kingdom"></interp>
