                        <interp inst="t17890114-44-person391" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , and to be directed to 
                     <persName id="t17890114-44-person392">
                        John
                         Hatchet
                     <interp inst="t17890114-44-person392" type="surname" value="Hatchet"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17890114-44-person392" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17890114-44-person392" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   and Co. of Long-acre, for payment of the sum of 5 l. 3 s. 6 d. for value received
            </rs>; which said bill of exchange is as follows -</p>
               <p>"No. 414. London,</p>
               <p>"Dec. 1st, 1788. Sir, please to pay</p>
               <p>"to 
               <persName id="t17890114-44-person393">
